WEBVTT

01:30.920 --> 01:35.009
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.780 --> 01:39.410
[2000]

02:19.200 --> 02:21.980
[Episode 34 The Two Sides of Life]

02:31.800 --> 02:32.329
Alright.

02:32.400 --> 02:33.170
Bride and groom, get ready.

02:33.170 --> 02:34.310
Look at the camera please.

02:34.310 --> 02:36.030
Alright. Three, two, one.

03:05.630 --> 03:06.160
Zhenzhu.

03:06.840 --> 03:08.150
Don't you think Xiaolan's wedding

03:08.150 --> 03:09.240
is a bit too plain?

03:10.030 --> 03:10.750
Though they're not doing

03:10.750 --> 03:11.840
the traditional bowing ceremony,

03:11.840 --> 03:13.080
they should at least, see—

03:13.080 --> 03:14.680
add a touch of red
to make it festive, right?

03:14.680 --> 03:15.520
Do the elders

03:15.750 --> 03:17.750
from both sides
not have a problem with this?

03:17.750 --> 03:19.560
Xiaolan told Cheng a long time ago

03:19.560 --> 03:21.420
that she wanted a simple wedding.

03:21.480 --> 03:23.120
Being surrounded by family and friends

03:23.120 --> 03:24.650
is the greatest happiness.

03:25.150 --> 03:27.560
Look, do Xiaolan's and Cheng's parents

03:27.710 --> 03:29.190
seem displeased to you?

03:31.190 --> 03:31.710
Sis Bai,

03:32.000 --> 03:32.710
this wine

03:32.850 --> 03:34.370
is said to be from Gangdao.

03:34.400 --> 03:35.020
It's very expensive.

03:35.020 --> 03:35.420
Try it.

03:35.630 --> 03:36.360
Here you are.

03:38.079 --> 03:38.870
You are...

03:39.079 --> 03:40.120
determined to be

03:40.120 --> 03:41.920
on the bride's side then, right?

03:41.960 --> 03:42.710
Of course.

03:42.710 --> 03:43.680
When they got engaged,

03:43.680 --> 03:44.480
I already said

03:44.520 --> 03:46.680
that Xiaolan would be my sister

03:46.710 --> 03:48.430
and Cheng my brother-in-law from then on.

03:48.430 --> 03:49.030
You really

03:49.240 --> 03:50.120
know when to act smart.

03:50.120 --> 03:51.780
You'll achieve great things.

03:53.430 --> 03:54.840
You Li, the two of you...

03:55.680 --> 03:56.280
Sis Bai,

03:56.520 --> 03:58.180
w-we're seeing how things go.

03:58.240 --> 03:58.910
If we get married,

03:58.910 --> 04:00.240
we'll definitely let you know.

04:00.240 --> 04:00.840
Okay.

04:00.840 --> 04:01.430
Then I'll be waiting

04:01.430 --> 04:02.760
for your wedding candy!

04:03.080 --> 04:03.520
Cheers.

04:03.520 --> 04:03.980
Cheers.

04:07.240 --> 04:08.030
When they

04:08.030 --> 04:09.210
first got together,

04:09.240 --> 04:11.040
I hoped they'd get married soon.

04:11.400 --> 04:12.760
But they were both too busy,

04:12.760 --> 04:14.620
so I didn't want to pressure them.

04:14.870 --> 04:16.269
Just let nature take its course.

04:16.269 --> 04:17.240
I used to be anxious too,

04:17.240 --> 04:18.560
but now I've stopped rushing the kids.

04:18.560 --> 04:19.160
She's just

04:19.240 --> 04:19.920
so fond

04:19.920 --> 04:20.680
of Xiaolan.

04:22.120 --> 04:22.830
Granny Yu.

04:23.920 --> 04:24.480
Let me take that.

04:24.480 --> 04:24.950
Have some fruit.

04:24.950 --> 04:25.800
Okay, hand it to me.

04:25.800 --> 04:26.830
Granny Yu, would you like some?

04:26.830 --> 04:28.830
Hello, uncles, aunties, Granny Yu.

04:29.190 --> 04:30.920
Today, I'm on the bride's side.

04:32.390 --> 04:32.990
Granny Yu.

04:33.240 --> 04:34.700
Do you enjoy this wedding?

04:34.720 --> 04:35.830
Do you think a wedding

04:35.830 --> 04:37.360
should be all red and bright

04:37.360 --> 04:38.760
with bowing ceremonies?

04:39.390 --> 04:41.190
Do I look like an old fogey to you?

04:41.270 --> 04:42.530
Xiaolan and Zhou Cheng

04:42.870 --> 04:44.870
want their wedding this way.

04:45.120 --> 04:46.720
What they like matters most.

04:46.950 --> 04:48.630
This wedding seems nice to me.

04:49.000 --> 04:49.730
It's elegant

04:50.040 --> 04:50.770
and natural.

04:51.480 --> 04:52.010
Exactly.

04:52.870 --> 04:53.630
Granny Yu

04:53.830 --> 04:55.000
has seen the world.

04:55.159 --> 04:56.610
She's very open-minded.

04:57.430 --> 04:59.159
I've long heard from Cheng

04:59.190 --> 05:01.050
about Granny Yu from Shengcheng.

05:02.240 --> 05:03.840
Today, as I finally meet you,

05:03.870 --> 05:05.260
I feel like we're already close.

05:05.260 --> 05:06.860
We truly clicked right away.

05:06.920 --> 05:07.390
Yes.

05:07.390 --> 05:08.160
If possible,

05:08.560 --> 05:09.750
we must gather and chat

05:09.750 --> 05:10.480
more often.

05:10.720 --> 05:11.270
-Sure.
-Right.

05:11.270 --> 05:11.870
Sure thing.

05:11.870 --> 05:13.360
When there's time, I'll take Granny Yu

05:13.360 --> 05:14.560
to Jingcheng by plane.

05:14.560 --> 05:15.510
No problem.

05:15.510 --> 05:17.120
When you get to Jingcheng,
I'll treat you to

05:17.120 --> 05:18.480
the best hotpot in the city.

05:18.480 --> 05:19.340
Eateries, too.

05:19.800 --> 05:21.160
Look, there they are.

05:21.240 --> 05:22.240
Hello, Granny Yu.

05:22.260 --> 05:23.070
We're here.

05:23.800 --> 05:24.680
Hello, Auntie.

05:25.120 --> 05:25.800
Hello, Auntie.

05:25.800 --> 05:27.320
Hello, Mr. Zhou and Mrs. Zhou.

05:27.320 --> 05:28.380
Hello, Mayor Tang.

05:30.070 --> 05:30.630
Look,

05:30.830 --> 05:31.510
over these years,

05:31.510 --> 05:32.630
Xiaolan has always exposed us

05:32.630 --> 05:34.030
to all sorts of new stuff.

05:34.240 --> 05:36.040
Such a beautifully decorated venue,

05:36.040 --> 05:36.560
see?

05:36.830 --> 05:37.950
All is like a dream,

05:38.120 --> 05:39.190
or a movie scene.

05:39.190 --> 05:39.920
Isn't it?

05:39.920 --> 05:40.720
Xiaolan

05:40.950 --> 05:41.870
always

05:41.870 --> 05:43.320
brings us surprises.

05:43.390 --> 05:44.190
That's right.

05:44.409 --> 05:44.940
She does.

05:44.950 --> 05:46.150
Here comes the bride!

05:56.920 --> 05:58.380
-Here she is!
-Here she is!

06:07.270 --> 06:08.270
You're gorgeous!

06:08.630 --> 06:10.120
Let's welcome the groom!

06:20.920 --> 06:22.560
-So handsome!
-Bravo!

06:30.000 --> 06:30.830
Why don't they

06:30.830 --> 06:32.310
walk down the aisle together?

06:32.310 --> 06:34.110
Isn't it bad to do it separately?

06:34.190 --> 06:35.060
It's a tradition

06:35.060 --> 06:37.360
for the bride to make an entrance
with her father.

06:37.360 --> 06:38.510
But now, Xiaolan has asked

06:38.510 --> 06:40.240
her mother to walk her down

06:40.830 --> 06:41.680
the aisle.

06:41.870 --> 06:42.190
Go ahead.

06:42.190 --> 06:42.870
Hurry, go quickly.

06:42.870 --> 06:43.409
I'm going then.

06:43.409 --> 06:44.010
Off you go.

06:48.430 --> 06:49.600
Who made that wedding dress?

06:49.600 --> 06:50.460
It's stunning.

06:50.830 --> 06:51.560
Chen.

06:51.920 --> 06:53.600
Teresa, why would you come?

06:53.830 --> 06:55.270
It's just been one month, right?

06:55.270 --> 06:56.310
I thought I must attend

06:56.310 --> 06:57.440
Xiaolan's wedding.

06:57.560 --> 06:58.040
Chen,

06:58.270 --> 06:59.670
you really put your heart

06:59.680 --> 07:00.680
into making this wedding dress.

07:00.680 --> 07:02.070
I certainly had to help Xia hold

07:02.070 --> 07:04.000
the most beautiful wedding of all.

07:06.390 --> 07:06.870
Mom.

07:07.360 --> 07:07.890
Xiaolan.

07:09.800 --> 07:10.730
Are you nervous?

07:11.510 --> 07:12.310
No, I'm not.

07:13.480 --> 07:14.240
I know

07:14.750 --> 07:15.880
that your days ahead

07:16.230 --> 07:18.090
will be filled with abundant joy.

07:24.840 --> 07:26.270
The wedding will commence soon.

07:26.270 --> 07:28.190
Dear guests, please take your seats.

07:28.190 --> 07:28.720
Let's go.

07:28.830 --> 07:29.160
This way.

07:29.160 --> 07:29.830
Move along, please.

07:29.830 --> 07:30.290
Thanks.

07:36.080 --> 07:39.740
♪ Maybe all encounters in the world ♪

07:39.950 --> 07:44.230
♪ Are predetermined by destiny ♪

07:45.990 --> 07:50.950
♪ The opening and closing chapters
are written ♪

07:51.680 --> 07:54.990
♪ From when we first met ♪

07:55.659 --> 07:59.490
♪ Till now, though much has changed ♪

08:01.760 --> 08:06.640
♪ Our hearts remain unchanged ♪

08:07.390 --> 08:12.330
♪ Making a dream in your eyes ♪

08:13.220 --> 08:22.500
♪ Time passes by,
yet I still love you the same ♪

08:23.150 --> 08:28.010
♪ After traveling through the crowds
and dark tides ♪

08:28.620 --> 08:37.780
♪ We must embrace
with the weight of the moment ♪

08:38.960 --> 08:42.409
♪ If a short hug is all we can have ♪

08:42.770 --> 08:46.440
♪ As a challenge of fate ♪

08:49.130 --> 08:53.730
♪ I don't want you to have any regrets ♪

08:50.360 --> 08:50.890
Xiaolan,

08:51.550 --> 08:52.210
Zhou Cheng,

08:52.510 --> 08:53.910
I send you my best wishes.

08:54.200 --> 08:55.510
I hope the two of you will strive together

08:54.890 --> 08:57.830
♪ Let's break the barriers
of time and space ♪

08:55.790 --> 08:56.720
for progress,

08:57.630 --> 08:58.790
and be happy ever after.

08:58.340 --> 09:02.080
♪ However ridiculous or bizarre
things are ♪

09:04.770 --> 09:09.930
♪ I'm determined to stick with you ♪

09:09.120 --> 09:09.720
Auntie...

09:10.250 --> 09:15.530
♪ Making a dream in your eyes ♪

09:13.030 --> 09:13.510
Mom,

09:14.080 --> 09:14.880
rest assured.

09:15.630 --> 09:16.230
We will.

09:16.250 --> 09:25.760
♪ A smile of yours
holds my life in its way ♪

09:26.050 --> 09:31.050
♪ Traveling through time and space,
courage is all I have ♪

09:27.960 --> 09:30.720
Now, bride and groom,
please exchange rings.

09:31.520 --> 09:43.850
♪ I hope you'll understand
how my heart flips for you ♪

09:57.430 --> 10:00.960
♪ If a short hug is all we can have ♪

10:01.480 --> 10:02.480
Bravo!

10:01.590 --> 10:05.540
♪ As a challenge of fate ♪

10:02.480 --> 10:20.080
-Kiss each other!
-Kiss!

10:07.830 --> 10:12.740
♪ I don't want you to have any regrets ♪

10:13.190 --> 10:16.740
♪ Let's break the barriers
of time and space ♪

10:17.160 --> 10:21.130
♪ However ridiculous or bizarre
things are ♪

10:23.140 --> 10:28.130
♪ I'm determined to stick with you ♪

10:29.030 --> 10:33.980
♪ Making a dream in your eyes ♪

10:34.990 --> 10:43.860
♪ A smile of yours
holds my life in its way ♪

10:44.810 --> 10:49.700
♪ Traveling through time and space,
courage is all I have ♪

10:50.250 --> 11:02.490
♪ I hope you'll understand
how my heart flips for you ♪

11:15.940 --> 11:20.760
♪ All my beloved ones are around ♪

11:21.570 --> 11:24.910
♪ Right at this moment ♪

11:25.470 --> 11:29.460
♪ Happiness is clearly visible ♪

11:31.720 --> 11:36.460
♪ Holding hands,
we walk in a rain of petals ♪

11:39.520 --> 11:44.390
♪ Let's raise the glasses
filled with champagne and blessings ♪

11:45.380 --> 11:48.540
♪ Thank you for being with me ♪

11:49.290 --> 11:53.970
♪ And completing my life ♪

11:54.510 --> 12:00.640
♪ For my love, dance in the wind ♪

11:57.480 --> 11:58.550
In my previous life

11:58.750 --> 11:59.600
and this life,

12:00.440 --> 12:01.550
the best thing

12:01.190 --> 12:09.020
♪ The world blooms at your feet ♪

12:02.360 --> 12:04.200
that I could imagine

12:04.600 --> 12:06.260
doesn't get better than this.

12:09.120 --> 12:10.510
In the building of my own creation,

12:10.440 --> 12:16.660
♪ Let there be embraces;
smiles and tears are priceless ♪

12:11.080 --> 12:11.940
those who I love

12:12.600 --> 12:14.730
and those who love me are all around me.

12:17.130 --> 12:21.620
♪ Life is beautiful like a painting ♪

12:17.270 --> 12:18.600
Each of them is happy,

12:19.270 --> 12:20.600
and they're happy about

12:21.080 --> 12:22.480
me being happy at the same time.

12:22.480 --> 12:27.820
♪ Keep going;
happiness is all that matters ♪

12:24.960 --> 12:26.290
What I've always wanted

12:26.750 --> 12:27.720
and yearned for

12:29.240 --> 12:30.510
is a scene like this.

12:41.700 --> 12:48.150
♪ Shining heart,
let joy dissolve into the air ♪

12:48.540 --> 12:52.900
♪ Let our hearts roam in the sky ♪

12:54.120 --> 13:00.840
♪ Sway and dance,
with your heart toward the sun ♪

13:21.530 --> 13:25.930
[Gangdao]

13:44.670 --> 13:45.600
Are you sneaking around

13:45.600 --> 13:47.060
to try to scare me to death?

13:48.000 --> 13:49.840
Do you have friends in the mansion?

13:49.840 --> 13:50.670
Go ask them for me

13:50.670 --> 13:52.200
if the Master has returned.

13:52.480 --> 13:53.030
Yes.

13:55.000 --> 13:56.240
What a lousy maid.

14:11.330 --> 14:12.360
I'm telling you, guys,

14:12.360 --> 14:13.480
I've never been to a wedding

14:13.480 --> 14:15.030
as special as yours.

14:15.440 --> 14:16.790
I had so much fun.

14:16.890 --> 14:18.460
See, the wine was good,

14:18.750 --> 14:20.010
and there was dancing.

14:20.080 --> 14:22.140
The two of you danced so beautifully.

14:22.150 --> 14:23.390
Granny Yu, if you like it,

14:23.390 --> 14:24.510
we'll hold a wedding

14:24.510 --> 14:25.770
every day. How about that?

14:25.770 --> 14:26.230
I agree.

14:29.720 --> 14:32.270
After the wedding,

14:32.510 --> 14:34.640
a-are the two of you moving to my place?

14:35.510 --> 14:35.960
Yes.

14:36.240 --> 14:39.100
Then what about your place
at the Golden Sands Pool?

14:39.510 --> 14:40.720
Our place at the Golden Sands Pool

14:40.720 --> 14:42.080
is still under renovation.

14:42.080 --> 14:42.680
Granny Yu,

14:42.920 --> 14:44.240
I saved an apartment for you

14:44.240 --> 14:45.320
right downstairs from ours.

14:45.320 --> 14:46.290
In the future, you can stay there

14:46.290 --> 14:48.150
or at your old place as you please.

14:54.420 --> 14:55.820
Granny Yu, what's wrong?

14:55.910 --> 14:56.570
Easy, easy.

14:56.840 --> 14:58.000
Granny Yu, are you carsick?

14:58.000 --> 14:59.060
Shall we pull over?

15:00.910 --> 15:02.110
I'm not feeling well.

15:02.750 --> 15:03.840
Ge Jian, go to the hospital.

15:03.840 --> 15:04.670
Hurry, to the hospital.

15:04.670 --> 15:05.400
Okay, got it.

15:06.000 --> 15:06.600
Granny Yu!

15:21.360 --> 15:22.630
Please wait outside!

15:26.510 --> 15:26.960
Mom?

15:27.630 --> 15:28.290
Uncle Tang?

15:29.720 --> 15:30.670
Why are you here?

15:31.550 --> 15:32.550
I'm feeling terrible.

15:32.550 --> 15:34.270
We've thrown up several times.

15:34.270 --> 15:35.600
I can't take it anymore.

15:35.710 --> 15:39.040
Given our tolerance for alcohol,
we shouldn't be like this.

15:40.030 --> 15:41.270
We didn't reach our limits yet.

15:41.270 --> 15:42.170
Liu Fen, Tang Hong'en,

15:42.170 --> 15:42.870
come with me.

15:42.870 --> 15:43.440
Let's go.

15:43.440 --> 15:44.840
-Come on.
-Go over there.

15:45.360 --> 15:46.840
Don't worry. We'll just be in there.

15:46.840 --> 15:48.300
Call the police, Xiaolan.

15:59.790 --> 16:01.080
Ms. Zhang, are you okay?

16:01.080 --> 16:01.870
I'm fine.

16:14.030 --> 16:18.030
[Gangdao]

16:19.000 --> 16:19.790
Quiet down!

16:20.120 --> 16:21.650
Do not obstruct our duties!

16:24.080 --> 16:24.550
Fine.

16:24.870 --> 16:25.200
Yes.

16:27.790 --> 16:29.720
Master!

16:30.440 --> 16:32.360
How do we cope without you?

16:33.320 --> 16:34.670
What should we do?

16:37.670 --> 16:39.360
Stop crying!

16:39.790 --> 16:41.190
You're in a hospital now,

16:41.320 --> 16:42.320
not a market.

16:42.550 --> 16:43.630
Watch the kids!

16:43.840 --> 16:45.370
Why did you bring them here?

16:45.550 --> 16:47.410
Is this even a place for children?

16:47.630 --> 16:48.510
All that crying and howling...

16:48.510 --> 16:50.510
Are you putting on a show for others?

16:54.120 --> 16:54.790
Excuse me.

16:55.320 --> 16:56.150
How is Mr. Du?

16:56.360 --> 16:58.270
We are still resuscitating the patient.

16:58.270 --> 16:59.200
Can you please stop making

16:59.200 --> 17:00.000
so much noise?

17:00.360 --> 17:01.720
I'm sorry for that.

17:01.870 --> 17:02.800
Just keep quiet.

17:03.200 --> 17:04.530
Don't disrupt our work.

17:04.790 --> 17:05.589
My apologies.

17:05.750 --> 17:06.480
I'm so sorry.

17:06.790 --> 17:07.720
Please save him!

17:09.510 --> 17:10.510
Did you hear that?

17:10.550 --> 17:11.609
Stop making noise!

17:11.720 --> 17:12.760
You're such a disgrace.

17:12.760 --> 17:13.420
Go sit down!

17:15.750 --> 17:17.609
You all are such a pain in the neck.

17:33.480 --> 17:35.740
Inside, your husband's life is at stake.

17:35.920 --> 17:38.400
Outside, your son is still missing.

17:39.160 --> 17:39.890
Auntie Song,

17:40.400 --> 17:42.200
take good care of yourself.

17:45.750 --> 17:46.810
This is a hospital.

17:47.310 --> 17:48.570
Why make so much noise?

17:49.440 --> 17:50.790
Do you want everyone to think

17:50.790 --> 17:51.790
that we the Du family all have

17:51.790 --> 17:52.590
poor manners?

17:53.750 --> 17:55.110
Then what can we do now?

17:57.000 --> 17:58.200
What do you want to do?

18:00.480 --> 18:01.010
Mr. Du...

18:01.230 --> 18:02.070
How is Mr. Du?

18:02.270 --> 18:02.720
Mr. Du.

18:03.160 --> 18:03.560
Mr. Du!

18:03.680 --> 18:04.410
How is Mr. Du?

18:04.750 --> 18:06.360
Tell me. How is Mr. Du doing now?

18:06.360 --> 18:07.680
-Miss, calm down.
-Say something!

18:07.680 --> 18:08.160
Mr. Du!

18:08.350 --> 18:08.970
Mr. Du...

18:09.440 --> 18:10.110
Enough!

18:10.290 --> 18:11.830
We just got a complaint about us.

18:11.830 --> 18:13.590
The doctor also told us
not to make any noise.

18:13.590 --> 18:15.250
Mr. Du is being resuscitated!

18:20.070 --> 18:21.470
I can't bear to watch you.

18:28.510 --> 18:30.370
It's not time for you to mourn yet.

18:59.030 --> 18:59.560
Xiaolan.

19:18.720 --> 19:20.350
Mom and Uncle Tang have gone home.

19:20.350 --> 19:21.440
The doctor has prescribed medicine
for them.

19:21.440 --> 19:22.570
They should be fine.

19:23.070 --> 19:24.400
San and Wei are in more serious condition.

19:24.400 --> 19:25.920
They're getting IVs
at the No. 2 Hospital.

19:25.920 --> 19:26.980
I've asked around.

19:27.450 --> 19:29.450
The older guests are actually fine.

19:29.480 --> 19:30.350
The doctor suspects

19:30.350 --> 19:32.010
this is a food poisoning case.

19:33.310 --> 19:33.840
Xiaolan,

19:34.590 --> 19:35.920
are you feeling unwell?

19:38.880 --> 19:39.940
It was the red wine.

19:41.750 --> 19:42.720
Older people

19:42.920 --> 19:44.520
usually don't like red wine,

19:44.550 --> 19:46.540
so they're showing less or no symptoms.

19:46.540 --> 19:48.080
Granny Yu has
pre-existing medical conditions,

19:48.080 --> 19:49.940
so she's having a worse reaction.

19:52.030 --> 19:52.440
Hello.

19:52.750 --> 19:54.010
Who called the police?

19:55.550 --> 19:56.350
Me, I did.

19:57.200 --> 19:57.830
I suspect

19:58.200 --> 19:58.920
someone poisoned

19:58.920 --> 20:00.250
our wedding reception.

20:08.200 --> 20:10.130
Here is a copy of the purchase list.

20:10.170 --> 20:11.440
The items were procured
by different people

20:11.440 --> 20:12.770
from different places.

20:13.290 --> 20:14.350
Okay. Please stick around

20:14.350 --> 20:15.590
to assist with our investigation.

20:15.590 --> 20:16.520
Got it, officer.

20:17.270 --> 20:19.000
Take this list and look into it.

20:19.440 --> 20:19.970
Yes, sir.

20:23.070 --> 20:24.930
How is the situation at the venue?

20:24.960 --> 20:25.420
Ms. Xia,

20:25.830 --> 20:26.920
the police arrived quickly.

20:26.920 --> 20:28.050
The food at the venue

20:28.060 --> 20:29.440
hasn't been cleared yet.

20:29.440 --> 20:31.350
Samples are being taken of every dish.

20:31.350 --> 20:32.470
Whether this is food poisoning

20:32.470 --> 20:33.790
or intentional poisoning,

20:33.790 --> 20:35.450
there should be results soon.

20:36.240 --> 20:38.440
What about those who procured the things?

20:38.440 --> 20:40.000
I'm having them stay temporarily

20:40.000 --> 20:41.310
in the company dormitory.

20:41.310 --> 20:41.680
Okay.

20:42.160 --> 20:42.920
Tell them

20:43.200 --> 20:44.880
it's not that we don't trust them.

20:44.880 --> 20:46.550
This just has to be done
as so to assist the police

20:46.550 --> 20:47.950
with the investigation.

20:48.310 --> 20:49.400
They're all showing great understanding

20:49.400 --> 20:50.510
and hoping the root cause can be found

20:50.510 --> 20:51.640
as soon as possible.

20:51.750 --> 20:52.810
Thank you, Ge Jian.

20:53.510 --> 20:54.760
Keep me posted

20:54.790 --> 20:55.680
on any updates.

20:56.290 --> 20:57.090
Sure, Ms. Xia.

21:05.550 --> 21:06.360
Get some rest.

21:14.210 --> 21:15.670
Take a nap if you're tired.

21:15.830 --> 21:16.760
I'm here for you.

21:17.350 --> 21:18.080
Don't worry.

21:51.920 --> 21:52.850
Anything wrong?

21:53.550 --> 21:54.950
Did you have a nightmare?

21:59.310 --> 22:00.910
Yes. But by the time I woke up,

22:01.680 --> 22:03.280
I had forgotten everything.

22:04.830 --> 22:06.360
That said, I still remember

22:07.110 --> 22:08.440
that feeling of loss...

22:10.240 --> 22:11.350
and fear.

22:15.790 --> 22:17.790
Dreams are the opposite of reality.

22:18.200 --> 22:18.930
Don't worry.

22:19.920 --> 22:21.780
They just brought some food over.

22:22.030 --> 22:22.690
Grab a bite.

22:24.200 --> 22:24.830
I know

22:25.510 --> 22:26.070
you won't listen to me

22:26.070 --> 22:27.800
even if I tell you to go home now.

22:27.830 --> 22:28.890
Then just stay here

22:29.070 --> 22:30.600
and keep Granny Yu company.

22:30.750 --> 22:31.950
If anything comes up,

22:32.150 --> 22:33.910
Ge Jian and others will take care of it.

22:33.910 --> 22:34.910
Just don't worry.

22:38.480 --> 22:39.510
Being surrounded

22:40.440 --> 22:41.350
by family,

22:42.550 --> 22:44.010
friends, and the man I love

22:44.650 --> 22:45.450
feels so good.

22:49.070 --> 22:49.960
Zhou Cheng,

22:51.270 --> 22:52.440
I'm a very greedy.

22:53.580 --> 22:55.510
I don't want to lose what I have now.

22:59.000 --> 23:00.330
We are all there for you.

23:00.750 --> 23:01.680
We'll always be.

23:02.960 --> 23:04.360
You won't lose anything.

23:05.510 --> 23:06.310
Rest assured.

23:14.210 --> 23:18.280
[Gangdao]

23:27.270 --> 23:28.600
How is the Master today?

23:32.830 --> 23:33.590
I'm asking you

23:33.590 --> 23:35.250
how the Master is doing today!

23:40.720 --> 23:41.160
Vivi!

23:42.440 --> 23:43.770
How is the Master doing?

23:44.750 --> 23:46.310
He drowned,

23:46.310 --> 23:46.880
and...

23:47.680 --> 23:48.880
his head got injured.

23:49.480 --> 23:50.550
The doctor said...

23:53.030 --> 23:55.030
Can't you finish it before crying?

23:55.750 --> 23:56.810
The doctor said...

23:57.200 --> 23:58.880
he might never wake up...

24:00.200 --> 24:01.880
and be in a coma forever.

24:19.480 --> 24:20.200
Mr. Cheng,

24:21.030 --> 24:22.270
nobody knows when my old man

24:22.270 --> 24:23.400
will wake up.

24:24.000 --> 24:25.750
Now, the Du family is left leaderless

24:25.750 --> 24:26.610
in sheer chaos.

24:27.510 --> 24:28.640
Did my old man devise

24:29.270 --> 24:30.160
any contingency plans

24:30.160 --> 24:31.620
for a situation like this?

24:33.210 --> 24:34.000
Mr. Du did have

24:34.000 --> 24:35.600
a power of attorney written.

24:37.270 --> 24:38.960
Should he get into an accident

24:39.640 --> 24:40.920
and become unable to personally handle

24:40.920 --> 24:42.050
corporate affairs,

24:42.240 --> 24:43.570
whoever in the Du family

24:43.880 --> 24:44.880
holds shares

24:44.880 --> 24:45.920
of the group

24:47.220 --> 24:48.110
will be given the power

24:48.110 --> 24:49.840
to temporarily act in his role.

24:51.730 --> 24:53.990
When was this power of attorney written?

24:59.310 --> 25:00.030
Mr. Cheng,

25:01.550 --> 25:02.880
if I hadn't asked today,

25:03.400 --> 25:05.260
would you have ever brought it up?

25:05.640 --> 25:06.350
Would you just watch

25:06.350 --> 25:08.150
our stock price keep plummeting

25:08.400 --> 25:09.530
and not do anything?

25:10.070 --> 25:10.870
Young Master,

25:12.920 --> 25:13.720
me keeping it secret

25:13.720 --> 25:15.580
is a term of the power of attorney.

25:16.640 --> 25:18.110
Let me venture a guess.

25:18.510 --> 25:19.400
Mr. Du probably

25:19.590 --> 25:21.000
had concerns about

25:21.510 --> 25:22.640
leaving the company

25:23.000 --> 25:24.070
under the charge of a family member

25:24.070 --> 25:25.640
who has never showed care

25:25.640 --> 25:26.770
for its operations.

25:27.200 --> 25:28.400
Do attorneys like you

25:28.640 --> 25:29.350
all speak

25:29.350 --> 25:30.610
in such an obscure way?

25:31.870 --> 25:32.730
How about this?

25:33.110 --> 25:34.710
Let me ask you in another way.

25:35.200 --> 25:36.200
Now that Du Zhaoji

25:36.590 --> 25:37.550
has ruthlessly

25:37.550 --> 25:38.590
targeted his own father...

25:38.590 --> 25:39.390
Young Master,

25:39.680 --> 25:41.050
there is no proof of it yet.

25:41.050 --> 25:42.580
He has fled. Isn't it proof?

25:48.000 --> 25:50.110
I've worked for Mr. Du for many years.

25:50.830 --> 25:53.110
Professionally and personally,

25:53.480 --> 25:55.000
my advice to you is

25:55.510 --> 25:57.070
that you should focus on

25:57.350 --> 25:59.590
how to stabilize the group

26:00.920 --> 26:02.750
in the shortest time possible.

26:04.160 --> 26:05.560
As for the other matters,

26:06.030 --> 26:07.590
Mr. Du will attend to them himself

26:07.590 --> 26:08.750
when he wakes up.

26:09.720 --> 26:12.110
Even if he can't wake up,

26:12.440 --> 26:14.100
you should turn to the police.

26:16.070 --> 26:16.730
Certainly,

26:16.960 --> 26:17.760
Young Master,

26:18.160 --> 26:19.070
it's just a piece of advice

26:19.070 --> 26:19.720
from me.

26:20.750 --> 26:22.440
Since I'm being paid by the Du family,

26:22.440 --> 26:24.640
of course I would look out for all of you.

26:25.790 --> 26:27.150
Getting the company in order

26:27.150 --> 26:28.630
is the priority right now.

26:33.480 --> 26:34.110
Mr. Cheng,

26:35.550 --> 26:37.950
no wonder my old man
thinks so highly of you.

26:38.640 --> 26:39.400
You can do

26:40.110 --> 26:40.720
more than

26:40.750 --> 26:42.610
just an ordinary attorney's job.

26:43.200 --> 26:44.000
Young Master,

26:44.510 --> 26:46.370
if you take charge of the company,

26:48.000 --> 26:49.600
I'll naturally work for you.

26:53.110 --> 26:54.680
This concludes the reading

26:54.920 --> 26:57.160
of Mr. Du Chengrong's power of attorney.

26:57.160 --> 26:58.760
According to this document,

26:59.680 --> 27:01.510
currently, only Mr. Du Zhaohui

27:01.640 --> 27:03.100
holds shares of the group,

27:03.350 --> 27:04.070
so

27:04.720 --> 27:05.680
from today on,

27:06.350 --> 27:08.150
Mr. Du Zhaohui will temporarily

27:08.160 --> 27:10.490
serve as the acting chairman of the group.

27:15.510 --> 27:16.550
When was this power of attorney

27:16.550 --> 27:17.270
signed?

27:17.790 --> 27:18.550
Why did I never hear

27:18.550 --> 27:19.960
Chairman Du talk about it?

27:19.960 --> 27:21.220
Mr. Cao, are you saying

27:21.440 --> 27:23.750
that Chairman Du should
ask for your opinion

27:23.750 --> 27:25.480
every time he signs a document?

27:26.030 --> 27:26.560
Mr. Meng,

27:27.400 --> 27:28.730
what do you mean by that?

27:28.830 --> 27:30.360
I just asked you a question.

27:31.440 --> 27:32.400
Or rather,

27:33.270 --> 27:35.240
do you not trust Mr. Cheng?

27:36.790 --> 27:39.450
The group will be taken over
by the Young Master.

27:47.590 --> 27:48.200
Everyone.

27:49.640 --> 27:51.160
I have lots of things to do

27:51.160 --> 27:52.790
both in the group and the hospital.

27:52.790 --> 27:53.510
I really can't spend

27:53.510 --> 27:54.840
more time with you here.

27:55.880 --> 27:57.030
If any of you

27:57.350 --> 27:59.000
have doubts about this power of attorney

27:59.000 --> 28:01.310
or what Mr. Cheng said,

28:04.200 --> 28:05.310
go have your eyes

28:05.550 --> 28:06.950
and brains checked then.

28:18.750 --> 28:19.160
Okay.

28:21.270 --> 28:21.800
Alright.

28:22.240 --> 28:22.750
Got it.

28:27.000 --> 28:28.310
Your guess was correct.

28:28.310 --> 28:30.240
The problem did lie in the red wine.

28:30.550 --> 28:31.680
What about the food?

28:32.240 --> 28:33.440
Nothing wrong has been found

28:33.440 --> 28:34.480
about the food yet.

28:34.480 --> 28:35.540
Ge Jian just told me

28:35.750 --> 28:36.750
he had traced the winery

28:36.750 --> 28:38.200
that produced the red wine.

28:38.200 --> 28:39.730
It belongs to the Du family.

28:40.440 --> 28:41.240
The Du family?

28:42.550 --> 28:43.110
Ms. Xia!

28:43.510 --> 28:44.480
Someone delivered a letter

28:44.480 --> 28:45.640
and said it must be handed to you.

28:45.640 --> 28:48.040
He then left without saying anything else.

28:59.890 --> 29:00.950
It's Ye Xiaoqiong.

29:06.070 --> 29:06.720
Ms. Xia,

29:07.510 --> 29:09.440
by the time you receive this letter,

29:09.440 --> 29:10.970
I will have taken my revenge

29:11.480 --> 29:13.640
and left Gangdao already.

29:16.660 --> 29:17.780
Du Zhaohui has decided go straight

29:17.780 --> 29:19.510
and start a legitimate business?

29:19.510 --> 29:20.570
Then what about me?

29:21.090 --> 29:22.440
Am I supposed to rely on his charity

29:22.440 --> 29:23.240
in the future?

29:23.750 --> 29:25.280
Doesn't he like that woman?

29:25.550 --> 29:27.280
Why didn't he go to her wedding?

29:28.000 --> 29:29.590
They should've died together!

29:29.590 --> 29:30.350
Second Young Master...

29:30.350 --> 29:31.370
Go away!

29:40.440 --> 29:41.240
Two days ago,

29:41.240 --> 29:42.840
a call was made to the office.

29:43.000 --> 29:45.000
Hearing about Du Zhaoji's absence,

29:45.000 --> 29:46.400
the caller was panicked.

29:46.640 --> 29:48.170
Before the call was hung up,

29:48.240 --> 29:49.350
I heard them saying

29:49.400 --> 29:50.930
Vivi was out of contact too.

29:51.110 --> 29:54.240
I think that caller was probably
a staffer of the winery.

29:54.590 --> 29:55.240
I'm not sure

29:55.240 --> 29:56.640
if this is helpful to you,

29:56.960 --> 29:58.110
but there is nothing more

29:58.110 --> 29:59.240
I can do for you.

30:00.880 --> 30:01.640
Now,

30:02.180 --> 30:03.200
I'm off to seek out

30:03.200 --> 30:04.350
my next haven.

30:05.120 --> 30:07.450
I hope when we see each other again
one day,

30:07.640 --> 30:09.570
I'll still be the same Ye Xiaoqiong

30:10.230 --> 30:11.290
that you first met.

30:14.240 --> 30:14.900
Xiaoqiong,

30:15.940 --> 30:17.870
I'm sure you'll find your own path.

30:26.000 --> 30:26.640
Old Man,

30:27.830 --> 30:28.960
I've come to see you.

30:30.160 --> 30:30.930
Look at you,

30:31.550 --> 30:33.210
having so many women and sons.

30:33.720 --> 30:35.920
But once the power of attorney was read,

30:35.920 --> 30:37.050
they all scattered.

30:38.680 --> 30:39.810
At the end of the day,

30:40.240 --> 30:41.970
nobody but me came to visit you.

30:43.590 --> 30:44.650
Don't get me wrong.

30:45.110 --> 30:46.000
I'm not doing this because I am

30:46.000 --> 30:47.530
more loyal than the others.

30:47.680 --> 30:49.680
I've benefited from you, after all.

30:50.310 --> 30:52.160
I just have to play the part

30:52.680 --> 30:53.830
of a filial son.

31:04.750 --> 31:06.550
You deserve such suffering.

31:07.960 --> 31:09.090
You've had your fun.

31:10.480 --> 31:11.160
However,

31:11.640 --> 31:13.370
have you ever thought about us?

31:13.590 --> 31:14.240
Have you ever

31:14.240 --> 31:15.440
truly cared about us?

31:18.030 --> 31:18.550
How much do you

31:18.550 --> 31:20.280
actually know about our lives?

31:20.590 --> 31:21.110
For example,

31:21.110 --> 31:22.400
during the party

31:22.750 --> 31:23.950
for my 18th birthday,

31:24.440 --> 31:26.590
somebody boldly slipped drugs in my drink.

31:26.590 --> 31:28.320
I was nearly poisoned to death.

31:29.160 --> 31:30.790
Do you even know about

31:31.480 --> 31:33.080
that special birthday gift?

31:35.110 --> 31:35.750
Another incident

31:35.750 --> 31:37.550
happened when I was 19 years old.

31:37.750 --> 31:39.350
I had a drag race with others,

31:40.310 --> 31:42.110
and someone tampered with the brakes.

31:42.110 --> 31:42.480
No.

31:44.480 --> 31:46.610
Let me tell you a more recent incident.

31:46.960 --> 31:48.200
When I turned 24, I meant

31:48.200 --> 31:49.600
to do something serious.

31:50.310 --> 31:52.910
So I went with others to a pier
to inspect goods.

31:54.030 --> 31:57.030
Then suddenly,
I got caught in a gang fight

31:57.790 --> 32:00.270
and was nearly killed in the crossfire.

32:01.160 --> 32:03.350
I'm so lucky and blessed
to be able to sit here

32:03.350 --> 32:04.920
and talk to you today.

32:05.960 --> 32:07.030
Do you have any idea

32:07.310 --> 32:09.200
how many times I've been targeted?

32:09.200 --> 32:10.400
I'm not stupid.

32:11.880 --> 32:14.590
I know you're aware of
each assassination attempt

32:14.590 --> 32:15.720
against me.

32:19.240 --> 32:20.640
In fact, I owe you thanks.

32:23.510 --> 32:24.910
I know you kept testing me

32:26.310 --> 32:27.750
to see if I had the ability

32:28.270 --> 32:29.730
to take over the Du family.

32:30.550 --> 32:32.480
That actually made me stop caring.

32:33.110 --> 32:34.240
And because of that,

32:34.590 --> 32:35.990
I luckily escaped danger

32:36.400 --> 32:37.350
multiple times.

32:46.590 --> 32:47.350
Old Man,

32:48.960 --> 32:50.510
what exactly happened?

32:52.750 --> 32:55.010
How did you get yourself into this state?

33:09.440 --> 33:09.840
Hello?

33:10.640 --> 33:11.300
Du Zhaohui,

33:11.750 --> 33:13.350
your dad's still alive, right?

33:13.350 --> 33:14.070
Where is

33:14.440 --> 33:15.000
Xia Ziyu?

33:15.960 --> 33:16.760
Xia Ziyu is now

33:17.160 --> 33:18.090
in the hospital.

33:18.350 --> 33:19.610
She comes by every day,

33:20.160 --> 33:21.800
cries and puts on an act,

33:21.830 --> 33:23.880
trying to wake my comatose father.

33:24.440 --> 33:25.400
Pretending to show care

33:25.400 --> 33:27.330
for a man who might never wake up...

33:27.880 --> 33:28.640
I guess...

33:29.270 --> 33:30.750
for Xia Ziyu,

33:31.400 --> 33:32.000
the ICU

33:32.000 --> 33:33.310
is the safest place.

33:34.030 --> 33:34.480
Why?

33:34.920 --> 33:35.750
Do you also think she is

33:35.750 --> 33:37.080
related to this matter?

33:37.550 --> 33:38.920
I already told the police

33:38.920 --> 33:40.200
this must be the conspiracy

33:40.200 --> 33:41.200
of her and Brat Ji.

33:41.790 --> 33:42.850
But the police said

33:42.880 --> 33:43.640
they couldn't arrest them

33:43.640 --> 33:44.790
due to lack of evidence.

33:44.790 --> 33:46.790
I don't care about
the Du family's affairs.

33:46.790 --> 33:48.050
The only thing I'm sure

33:48.440 --> 33:50.570
is that Xia Ziyu must be the one who hurt

33:51.310 --> 33:52.570
my family and friends.

33:53.480 --> 33:54.110
Ms. Xia,

33:54.480 --> 33:56.740
don't forget she was driven crazy by you.

33:57.440 --> 33:58.240
She would've

33:59.310 --> 34:00.840
gone crazy even without me.

34:04.030 --> 34:06.160
Whether Du Chengrong will come to or not,

34:06.160 --> 34:06.750
the Du family

34:06.750 --> 34:08.210
is bound to get into a mess.

34:09.190 --> 34:09.790
By the way,

34:10.070 --> 34:11.130
how did your old man

34:11.320 --> 34:12.280
get injured?

34:13.190 --> 34:14.810
The only thing I know
is that he was on the way

34:14.810 --> 34:16.540
to acquire an antique that day.

34:23.920 --> 34:25.449
Why did you take this route?

34:26.429 --> 34:27.840
Traffic gets heavy on rainy days.

34:27.840 --> 34:29.639
This route can save us some time.

34:31.760 --> 34:33.090
Such terrible weather.

34:33.280 --> 34:34.760
How about we ask Mr. Qiu to postpone

34:34.760 --> 34:35.489
the meeting?

34:36.110 --> 34:36.710
Master,

34:37.230 --> 34:38.360
we're almost there.

34:55.400 --> 34:56.260
In such a hurry?

34:57.440 --> 34:59.840
Are you afraid
that I'd pull the plug on him?

34:59.840 --> 35:00.570
Don't worry.

35:01.110 --> 35:02.440
A brother of mine already

35:02.440 --> 35:03.440
made an attempt to kill our father.

35:03.440 --> 35:04.170
It's enough.

35:36.710 --> 35:37.970
Granny Yu needs to stay

35:38.230 --> 35:40.890
a few more days in the hospital
for observation.

35:41.510 --> 35:43.040
I underestimated my enemy.

35:44.590 --> 35:45.920
Never did it occur to me

35:46.920 --> 35:48.070
that she'd target my family

35:48.070 --> 35:48.920
and friends.

35:51.960 --> 35:53.030
When I first

35:53.760 --> 35:55.230
woke up

35:55.230 --> 35:56.490
in Xia Xiaolan's body,

35:57.230 --> 35:58.760
in front of me
was a group of Xia family members

35:58.760 --> 36:00.400
who wished I would die soon.

36:02.000 --> 36:04.200
I confronted them bravely at that time.

36:06.000 --> 36:07.030
In the time and space

36:07.030 --> 36:08.400
where I used to be,

36:08.880 --> 36:09.880
I already grew accustomed

36:09.880 --> 36:11.940
to being indifferent to everything.

36:14.440 --> 36:15.480
Only on that day

36:16.230 --> 36:17.110
did I realize

36:18.560 --> 36:19.620
that venting anger

36:20.510 --> 36:21.240
felt so good.

36:22.480 --> 36:24.440
Why don't you just go die?

36:25.230 --> 36:27.070
Protecting her now, aren't you?

36:29.400 --> 36:30.600
You terrible old hag,

36:30.760 --> 36:31.710
watching your mouth

36:31.710 --> 36:32.960
would be the only good deed
you can do for yourself.

36:32.960 --> 36:34.480
She's calling me a terrible old hag.

36:34.480 --> 36:35.440
Xiaolan, what are you saying?

36:35.440 --> 36:36.440
Is this Xia household

36:36.440 --> 36:38.000
too small for you now?

36:38.220 --> 36:39.480
Yeah, this lousy place

36:39.590 --> 36:41.650
really can't handle someone like me.

36:44.230 --> 36:44.840
At that time,

36:44.840 --> 36:46.840
it was my mom who gave me the courage.

36:50.000 --> 36:50.880
Gradually,

36:51.680 --> 36:53.140
I didn't just protect her.

36:54.760 --> 36:56.360
I actually began to love her.

36:57.880 --> 36:58.960
Later on,

37:00.670 --> 37:01.730
you guys showed up.

37:05.000 --> 37:05.660
Zhou Cheng,

37:08.590 --> 37:10.110
if I own everything

37:11.070 --> 37:11.840
but the power

37:11.840 --> 37:13.500
to protect those I care about,

37:14.510 --> 37:16.710
what will be the point of having so much?

37:19.840 --> 37:21.000
I've forgotten and become unable

37:21.000 --> 37:22.000
to recall clearly

37:23.150 --> 37:24.610
many things from the past.

37:26.400 --> 37:28.200
But I still remember the feeling

37:29.230 --> 37:30.960
of being lonely and helpless.

37:32.710 --> 37:34.440
I am the brave person I am now

37:37.710 --> 37:38.920
because of all of you.

37:41.190 --> 37:41.720
Xiaolan,

37:43.840 --> 37:44.710
love is mutual.

37:46.670 --> 37:47.730
Everyone loves you

37:48.920 --> 37:49.550
and feels the love

37:49.550 --> 37:50.510
you give away.

37:51.880 --> 37:52.540
Therefore,

37:58.230 --> 37:59.760
don't feel burdened at all.

38:04.400 --> 38:05.860
Lately, I've been feeling

38:06.280 --> 38:08.210
that something is about to happen.

38:09.670 --> 38:10.320
If...

38:11.760 --> 38:13.160
I mean, hypothetically,

38:14.110 --> 38:15.970
-if this matter...
-Don't worry.

38:16.400 --> 38:17.730
No matter what happens,

38:18.960 --> 38:20.160
I'll be there for you.

38:23.920 --> 38:25.250
But what if I disappear?

38:33.600 --> 38:35.700
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

38:35.730 --> 38:40.000
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

38:40.430 --> 38:42.840
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

38:42.990 --> 38:47.600
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

38:47.940 --> 38:51.900
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

38:51.930 --> 38:55.980
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

38:56.360 --> 38:57.320
No matter where you are,

38:56.810 --> 39:01.120
♪ Together, forever ♪

38:59.880 --> 39:01.080
I'll always find you.

39:22.420 --> 39:23.450
[Dynasty in turmoil again: Du Chengrong,
head of the Du family, bizarrely drowns]

39:25.420 --> 39:27.130
[Chairman of Chengrong Group,
Du Chengrong]

39:33.190 --> 39:33.720
Alright.

39:34.920 --> 39:35.520
Let's eat.

39:36.320 --> 39:37.720
This man Du Chengrong...

39:40.190 --> 39:41.400
I heard from Xiaolan

39:41.670 --> 39:43.550
there was a fight within the Du family.

39:43.550 --> 39:44.110
Du Chengrong's second son

39:44.110 --> 39:45.910
has been missing for a long time.

39:46.110 --> 39:47.670
Given the Du family's background,

39:47.670 --> 39:49.320
it's no surprise for such a thing

39:49.320 --> 39:49.960
to happen.

39:51.400 --> 39:52.660
Look what it says here.

39:53.150 --> 39:55.010
Du Chengrong got into an accident

39:55.150 --> 39:57.350
on the way to negotiate an antique deal.

39:57.400 --> 39:59.480
Granny Yu's son happens to do

39:59.480 --> 40:01.140
antique business in Gangdao.

40:01.550 --> 40:02.800
When Xiaolan was there last time,

40:02.800 --> 40:04.260
she had a meeting with him.

40:05.560 --> 40:06.360
For unknown reasons,

40:06.360 --> 40:08.160
he just wouldn't come back here.

40:08.200 --> 40:09.600
I just don't understand.

40:09.670 --> 40:11.190
He hasn't seen his own mother

40:11.190 --> 40:12.190
for several decades.

40:12.190 --> 40:14.590
How could he have the heart
not to come back?

40:15.030 --> 40:15.770
People...

40:15.880 --> 40:18.080
find it the hardest to face themselves.

40:18.630 --> 40:19.400
Everything else

40:19.400 --> 40:20.400
is just an excuse.

40:21.110 --> 40:22.190
Do you mean deep down,

40:22.190 --> 40:23.990
he's still clinging to the past?

40:24.500 --> 40:26.000
Xiaolan informed him

40:26.030 --> 40:27.320
of Granny Yu's sickness

40:27.320 --> 40:28.440
and asked him to come back.

40:28.440 --> 40:29.640
But he just wouldn't.

40:29.920 --> 40:30.590
He said...

40:31.350 --> 40:32.880
he couldn't face Granny Yu.

40:33.800 --> 40:34.960
Does it mean if he can never

40:34.960 --> 40:36.250
move on from the past,

40:36.280 --> 40:37.940
he won't see his mother again?

40:39.670 --> 40:41.470
Granny Yu doesn't say anything,

40:41.550 --> 40:42.400
but she surely misses

40:42.400 --> 40:43.260
her son, right?

40:43.590 --> 40:44.650
What can we do then?

40:44.800 --> 40:46.360
Nothing anyone says will help

40:46.360 --> 40:47.960
if he can't get over the past.

40:48.190 --> 40:49.230
All we can do is spend

40:49.230 --> 40:50.630
more time with Granny Yu.

40:50.800 --> 40:52.030
Granny Yu will be discharged today.

40:52.030 --> 40:53.760
I'll stay at her place tonight.

40:54.400 --> 40:55.670
So I'll have to be home alone?

40:55.670 --> 40:57.530
Just stay put and watch the house.

40:58.190 --> 40:58.840
When you bring

40:58.840 --> 40:59.840
the old lady home, make sure

40:59.840 --> 41:01.170
she gets plenty of rest.

41:01.710 --> 41:02.190
Thanks.

41:03.150 --> 41:04.840
I must make you chicken soup back home.

41:04.840 --> 41:06.240
You need it for recovery.

41:22.440 --> 41:23.640
What is he doing here?

41:24.000 --> 41:24.440
Who?

41:25.400 --> 41:27.140
Xu Zhongyi's assistant, Chai Hai.

41:27.140 --> 41:28.470
You go pick up Granny Yu.

41:29.590 --> 41:30.030
Okay.

41:34.190 --> 41:34.720
Chai Hai.

41:37.760 --> 41:39.420
Before you disturb Granny Yu,

41:39.480 --> 41:40.410
talk to me first.

41:41.920 --> 41:42.360
Okay.

41:42.750 --> 41:46.660
[Shengcheng Municiple People's Hospital]

41:45.960 --> 41:46.490
Chai Hai,

41:47.030 --> 41:48.400
I remember asking Xu Zhongyi

41:48.400 --> 41:49.800
to come to Shengcheng.

41:50.280 --> 41:51.000
His mother

41:51.000 --> 41:52.070
fell seriously ill.

41:52.070 --> 41:53.870
Isn't she worth a visit from him?

41:54.550 --> 41:55.150
Ms. Xia,

41:55.530 --> 41:56.930
Mr. Xu would love to come,

41:57.230 --> 41:58.880
but he's been swamped lately.

41:58.880 --> 42:00.550
He just went abroad last week
to pick up goods.

42:00.550 --> 42:01.280
It's not certain yet

42:01.280 --> 42:02.340
when he'll be back.

42:02.710 --> 42:03.800
Xu Zhongyi...

42:04.400 --> 42:06.400
can afford a plane ticket, can't he?

42:07.150 --> 42:07.960
Mr. Xu said

42:08.510 --> 42:09.070
he'd surely find time

42:09.070 --> 42:11.200
to visit Shengcheng when he came back.

42:11.320 --> 42:12.710
This... is what he had me

42:12.710 --> 42:13.880
bring to his mother.

42:14.190 --> 42:15.230
Take it back.

42:16.190 --> 42:16.800
Also,

42:17.630 --> 42:19.360
pass a message to Mr. Qiu for me.

42:20.190 --> 42:22.550
Tell him that during all these years
in Shengcheng,

42:22.550 --> 42:24.680
Granny Yu never needs stuff like this.

42:25.110 --> 42:26.640
I'll take everything away,

42:27.230 --> 42:28.160
except for this.

42:28.400 --> 42:29.200
Mr. Qiu told me

42:29.480 --> 42:32.340
specifically to return this
to its original owner.

42:37.670 --> 42:38.800
Please do me a favor.

42:43.070 --> 42:43.960
Walk slowly.

42:44.230 --> 42:44.630
Okay.

42:45.480 --> 42:46.440
How do you feel?

42:47.070 --> 42:47.730
I feel fine.

42:47.840 --> 42:48.170
Good.

42:49.510 --> 42:50.840
What are you doing here?

42:52.280 --> 42:53.190
Wait here for a moment.

42:53.190 --> 42:53.800
I'll go get the car.

42:53.800 --> 42:54.130
Okay.

42:54.760 --> 42:56.230
Let's wait till he drives the car over

42:56.230 --> 42:57.290
before we head out.

42:59.110 --> 42:59.960
It's windy outside.

42:59.960 --> 43:01.290
Let's wait here for now.

43:01.480 --> 43:01.880
Okay.

43:02.710 --> 43:04.190
Let me fix your scarf.

43:08.280 --> 43:09.610
Granny Yu, you're back.

43:10.230 --> 43:10.690
Come on.

43:11.880 --> 43:12.480
Come here.

43:12.510 --> 43:14.230
How is it
that an old lady like me receives

43:14.230 --> 43:15.230
such a special treatment today?

43:15.230 --> 43:15.670
Look.

43:17.590 --> 43:18.720
If you like the food,

43:18.880 --> 43:20.480
I'll cook for your every day.

43:20.480 --> 43:21.230
It's true

43:21.880 --> 43:22.960
that I've always wondered

43:22.960 --> 43:24.400
what Fen's daily diet

43:24.400 --> 43:25.110
is like.

43:25.360 --> 43:26.330
It's wonderful.

43:26.360 --> 43:27.110
I've even gained weight.

43:27.110 --> 43:27.630
Really?

43:27.690 --> 43:28.710
Going on a diet is a trend now.

43:28.710 --> 43:30.630
But Fen is not fat at all. She's so slim.

43:30.630 --> 43:32.280
There is a soup and two dishes coming.

43:32.280 --> 43:33.470
Rest for a bit, Granny Yu.

43:33.470 --> 43:34.480
Everyone, take a seat.

43:34.480 --> 43:36.140
I'll get you inside for a rest.

43:37.320 --> 43:38.180
Do you think...

43:38.360 --> 43:39.690
Xu Zhongyi saw all that?

43:40.360 --> 43:41.090
I don't know.

43:41.590 --> 43:42.230
But I think

43:42.800 --> 43:43.480
he must be around.
